1503
02:17:07,459 --> 02:17:10,959
Of course.
There are many ways.

1504
02:17:13,750 --> 02:17:17,250
Yes we'll go away from
this country tonight.

1505
02:18:18,625 --> 02:18:22,709
You don't have to do this..

1506
02:18:24,209 --> 02:18:27,042
I want to.

1507
02:18:27,542 --> 02:18:32,417
Sukhi, this might end badly.

1508
02:18:32,917 --> 02:18:38,709
Without you guys it will end
for me anyway..

1509
02:18:39,209 --> 02:18:42,709
Idiot.
Come.

1510
02:18:51,625 --> 02:18:55,125
Ajay passed away.
But his death won't go in vain, ma.

1511
02:19:03,084 --> 02:19:09,000
What is it about these boys
that make them have no fear?

1512
02:19:09,500 --> 02:19:12,250
I think some times a person
can be pushed so..

1513
02:19:12,750 --> 02:19:18,417
.. far that they reach a place beyond fear.

1514
02:19:18,917 --> 02:19:22,459
A place where we find
a strange peace where you..

1515
02:19:22,959 --> 02:19:28,500
.. free yourselves to do the right thing.

1516
02:19:29,000 --> 02:19:34,167
And sometimes that's the hardest thing to do.

1517
02:19:34,367 --> 02:19:35,984
Welcome back to Raat Baaki Baat Baaki.

1518
02:19:36,584 --> 02:19:39,417
This is Rahul, and you've tuned
in to your favourite radio show..

1519
02:19:39,917 --> 02:19:43,417
