Put you on air?

1524
02:21:15,570 --> 02:21:17,111
Yeah, now! Live.

1525
02:21:17,611 --> 02:21:20,236
I want to go on air. Live.
Is it some kind of a joke?

1526
02:21:20,736 --> 02:21:23,611
