I'll lose my job.

1527
02:21:24,111 --> 02:21:26,528
It's payback time.

1528
02:21:27,028 --> 02:21:32,153
Hey! It's your station.
Unreal man!

1529
02:21:32,653 --> 02:21:34,653
Gun..
He's got a gun!

1530
02:21:35,153 --> 02:21:37,945
Karan you go in.
I'll handle it.

1531
02:21:38,445 --> 02:21:46,736
Keep the show on.
Don't mess with us.

1532
02:21:47,236 --> 02:21:52,528
Come on.. leave, don't worry,
nothing will happen.

1533
02:21:53,028 --> 02:21:56,278
Paaji is anyone inside?

1534
02:21:56,778 --> 02:22:01,028
Uncle-ji run.
Don't stop.

1535
02:22:01,528 --> 02:22:06,945
Gun.. Security he's got a gun!

1536
02:22:07,445 --> 02:22:09,028
Don't be a wise guy.

1537
02:22:09,528 --> 02:22:12,028
Everybody leave!
Out! Move!

1538
02:22:12,528 --> 02:22:15,611
Everybody leave! Out! Move!

1539
02:22:16,111 --> 02:22:19,528
Don't panic we won't harm anyone.

1540
02:22:20,028 --> 02:22:22,778
Move! Move! Move!
Nothing will happen.

1541
02:22:23,278 --> 02:22:28,403
Move, Nothing will happen to you.

1542
02:22:28,903 --> 02:22:29,570
Nothing will happen to you,
don't worry, move..

1543
02:22:30,070 --> 02:22:33,570
Hurry up, quick!
Till downstairs.

1544
02:22:50,445 --> 02:22:52,528
The time is 6:05 a.m. My name is Rahul..

1545
02:22:53,028 --> 02:22:56,445
