"The night is still young".

1546
02:22:56,945 --> 02:22:59,736
Today I've got a surprise guest for you.

1547
02:23:00,236 --> 02:23:02,403
An old friend of mine
Karan Singhania who just..

1548
02:23:02,903 --> 02:23:06,403
.. dropped in to say something
to all of you..

1549
02:23:12,311 --> 02:23:16,020
My name is Karan Singhania..
My friends and I..

1550
02:23:16,820 --> 02:23:19,986
