1551
02:23:20,486 --> 02:23:24,486
I repeat we killed the Defence Minister..

1552
02:23:24,986 --> 02:23:28,153
Ravi take me to the radio station quickly.
Hurry up!

1553
02:23:28,653 --> 02:23:34,278
We are not terrorists.
We aren't backed by any foreign organisation.

1554
02:23:34,778 --> 02:23:37,736
We don't even belong to
any political group..

1555
02:23:38,236 --> 02:23:40,820
We're just five students from
Delhi University.

1556
02:23:41,320 --> 02:23:44,320
We killed the Defense Ministe
 because he murdered..

1557
02:23:44,820 --> 02:23:49,361
.. our friend Flight Lieutenant
Ajay Rathod..

1558
02:23:49,861 --> 02:23:52,986
.. and many other Air Force pilots..

1559
02:23:53,486 --> 02:23:55,903
We killed him because after
he murdered Ajay,

1560
02:23:56,403 --> 02:23:58,903
.. he murdered his name..

1561
02:23:59,403 --> 02:24:02,403
Ajay's mother who not only sacrificed him..

1562
02:24:02,903 --> 02:24:05,486
.. but also her husband..

1563
02:24:05,986 --> 02:24:12,695
.. right now, is fighting for her life..

1564
02:24:13,195 --> 02:24:18,653
A Defence Minister is supposed
to safegaurd a nation. Not sell it.

1565
02:24:19,153 --> 02:24:22,070
Who will stop them?
Law.

1566
02:24:22,570 --> 02:24:23,570
Men like the Defence Minister aren't just..

1567
02:24:24,070 --> 02:24:26,070
.. above the law..
they control it.

1568
02:24:26,570 --> 02:24:28,986
We killed the Defence Minister because..

1569
02:24:29,486 --> 02:24:31,695
.. he was roaming scot-free..

1570
02:24:32,195 --> 02:24:35,028
.. even after committing such a big crime.

1571
02:24:35,528 --> 02:24:40,736
What we have done is wrong,
may be it's a crime.

1572
02:24:41,236 --> 02:24:47,111
But we could not see all this.
We have come here to surrender.

1573
02:24:47,611 --> 02:24:49,195
We have come here to tell everyone..

1574
02:24:49,695 --> 02:24:52,528
.. that we must do something.

1575
02:24:53,028 --> 02:24:58,195
We all have to do something.

1576
02:24:58,395 --> 02:24:59,995
We've just received news that the Defence..

1577
02:25:00,695 --> 02:25:02,653
.. Minister's assassins are hiding in the All India Radio building.

1578
02:25:03,153 --> 02:25:05,361
Karan Singhania and his friends are still with us.

1579
02:25:05,861 --> 02:25:13,486
Listeners can call in on
3291777.

1580
02:25:13,986 --> 02:25:17,486
Until then..

1581
02:25:23,857 --> 02:25:27,357
It's done.

1582
02:25:34,982 --> 02:25:38,107
"Hey, dude!"

1583
02:25:38,607 --> 02:25:46,440
"I just realized."

1584
02:25:46,940 --> 02:25:54,357
"There's a fire burning within me."

1585
02:25:54,857 --> 02:25:58,149
"It's a new dawn."

1586
02:25:58,649 --> 02:26:02,107
"I can feel its light."

1587
02:26:02,607 --> 02:26:08,732
"Burn so bright, I could,
scorch the sun."

1588
02:26:09,232 --> 02:26:16,732
"Cause I'm face to face with the light."

1589
02:26:17,232 --> 02:26:25,124
"Cause I'm face to face with the light."

1590
02:26:26,024 --> 02:26:37,440
"The dream I once lost,
I've found."

1591
02:26:37,940 --> 02:26:41,482
"It's blooming."

1592
02:26:41,982 --> 02:26:49,524
"It's melting."

1593
02:26:50,024 --> 02:26:57,232
"Notes arranging."

1594
02:26:57,732 --> 02:27:06,432
"Into a whole new melody."

1595
02:27:07,232 --> 02:27:10,649
Will they give us good food in jail?

1596
02:27:11,149 --> 02:27:14,649
Food?
Next he'll want beer.

1597
02:27:21,774 --> 02:27:23,440
You guys have become famous.

1598
02:27:23,940 --> 02:27:26,440
Calls are pouring in from all over the country.

1599
02:27:26,940 --> 02:27:29,149
Come on!
They want to talk to you..

1600
02:27:29,649 --> 02:27:34,065
Your news has spread everywhere.

1601
02:27:34,565 --> 02:27:36,315
Police!
- Police!

1602
02:27:36,815 --> 02:27:38,315
This is unreal man.
How did this happen?

1603
02:27:38,815 --> 02:27:41,315
Where did they come from?
This will ruin my career..

1604
02:27:41,815 --> 02:27:44,149
Quiet!
You move, Karan, get him out.

1605
02:27:44,649 --> 02:27:46,482
Karan you get on air..
We don't have much time..

1606
02:27:46,982 --> 02:27:48,440
They will catch us within Fifteen minutes..

1607
02:27:48,940 --> 02:27:50,190
.. you go and say whatever you want.

1608
02:27:50,690 --> 02:27:54,190
Take care.

1609
02:27:56,565 --> 02:27:57,899
The Delhi police have reached the spot and..

1610
02:27:58,399 --> 02:28:00,315
.. are rescuing civilians trapped in the building.

1611
02:28:00,815 --> 02:28:02,482
The responsibility of the Minister's murder..

1612
02:28:02,982 --> 02:28:04,065
.. has just reached Calcutta.

1613
02:28:04,565 --> 02:28:07,149
I am in Bangalore and
as you can see all the students..

1614
02:28:07,649 --> 02:28:09,565
.. reporting from Mumbai's Churchgate area..

1615
02:28:10,065 --> 02:28:11,649
.. reporting from Cotton College, Guwahati.

1616
02:28:12,149 --> 02:28:13,732
.. reporting from S. P. College, Srinagar..

1617
02:28:14,232 --> 02:28:15,357
.. reporting from Lucknow University..

1618
02:28:15,857 --> 02:28:18,274
.. and the reactions are coming very fast.

1619
02:28:18,574 --> 02:28:21,324
Hi, my name is Prakash.
And I want to congratulate you.

1620
02:28:22,024 --> 02:28:23,065
You did the right thing by killing him.

1621
02:28:23,565 --> 02:28:27,065
All our ministers should be lined up and shot.

1622
02:28:27,565 --> 02:28:30,899
Mr. Prakash, who all will you shoot?

1623
02:28:31,399 --> 02:28:34,649
These corrupt ministers are
a reflection of our society.

1624
02:28:35,149 --> 02:28:36,524
We've chosen them.

1625
02:28:37,024 --> 02:28:39,274
If they are corrupt then so are we.

1626
02:28:39,774 --> 02:28:42,107
We need to change ourselves
to bring about a change.

1627
02:28:42,607 --> 02:28:43,899
Hello this is Principal Sharma,
Government..

1628
02:28:44,399 --> 02:28:46,940
.. Higher Secondary School from Indore..

1629
02:28:47,440 --> 02:28:48,399
You have set a bad example by taking..

1630
02:28:48,899 --> 02:28:52,190
.. the law into your own hands.

1631
02:28:52,690 --> 02:28:56,607
You're right sir.
We're sorry.

1632
02:28:57,107 --> 02:28:59,565
But give me the name of one politician who..

1633
02:29:00,065 --> 02:29:03,399
.. has gone to jail for his crimes.

1634
02:29:03,899 --> 02:29:05,774
Who else is on your hit-list?

1635
02:29:06,274 --> 02:29:08,482
We have no hit-list.

1636
02:29:08,982 --> 02:29:10,940
How do you feel after killing
the Defence Minister?

1637
02:29:11,440 --> 02:29:14,982
We had no enmity.
It's not that we killed him and have cooled down.

1638
02:29:15,482 --> 02:29:18,982
We still have the rage within.

1639
02:29:35,315 --> 02:29:39,357
If you get caught you'll be hanged.
Aren't you afraid?

1640
02:29:39,857 --> 02:29:43,524
No.

1641
02:29:44,024 --> 02:29:48,149
As you can see the Black Cats
have reached the place.

1642
02:29:48,649 --> 02:29:54,149
And the boys who have killed
the minister are still inside.

1643
02:29:54,649 --> 02:29:56,982
Karan, I don't know whether
you did right or wrong..

1644
02:29:57,482 --> 02:30:01,607
..while we applaud your courage,
do you think you will get out alive?

1645
02:30:02,107 --> 02:30:05,440
Death doesn't scare us.

1646
02:30:05,940 --> 02:30:09,440
No one should remain alive.
I don't want any survivor. - Yes sir.

1647
02:30:31,024 --> 02:30:33,274
Sukhi

1648
02:30:33,774 --> 02:30:35,524
Bullets are being shot in
All India Radio.

1649
02:30:36,024 --> 02:30:39,524
Ravi, please make him go quickly.

1650
02:30:45,774 --> 02:30:48,774
Shit! They're shooting at us DJ!
They're shooting at us!

1651
02:30:49,274 --> 02:30:55,149
Shut up for a second!

1652
02:30:55,649 --> 02:31:00,399
