They think we're armed.

1653
02:31:00,899 --> 02:31:04,399
Don't worry,
I will handle it, Don't worry.

1654
02:31:17,482 --> 02:31:24,357
No.. Kill me.. Kill me..

1655
02:31:24,857 --> 02:31:34,607
Sukhi.. No Sukhi!
What did you do! What did you do?

1656
02:31:35,107 --> 02:31:44,065
Shit DJ! Just when I was getting good with the girls..
- No, Sukhi..

1657
02:31:44,565 --> 02:31:48,065
No, Sukhi..

1658
02:32:02,649 --> 02:32:04,149
My name is Indra. What's the difference..

1659
02:32:04,649 --> 02:32:05,857
.. between you and terrorists?

1660
02:32:06,357 --> 02:32:10,257
There's a big difference..
terrorists kill innocents, we didn't..

1661
02:32:19,857 --> 02:32:23,357
Aslam..

1662
02:32:25,899 --> 02:32:28,690
..close the door.
Quick!

1663
02:32:29,190 --> 02:32:32,690
We are not terrorists.
Why don't they..

1664
02:33:22,099 --> 02:33:25,224
It's not a lust for blood..
it's a matter of justice!

1665
02:33:25,324 --> 02:33:27,099
Why are bullets being used
when it's clear..

1666
02:33:27,899 --> 02:33:30,690
.. that these are college students?

1667
02:33:31,190 --> 02:33:34,690
This is Shomu Bose from
All India Radio for NDTV.

1668
02:35:16,280 --> 02:35:19,863
No matter what you do, this country..

1669
02:35:20,363 --> 02:35:28,238
