It has no future.

1670
02:35:28,738 --> 02:35:32,238
No country is perfect.
You've got to make it perfect.

1671
02:35:37,705 --> 02:35:44,705
Join the police,
military, IAS..

1672
02:35:45,405 --> 02:35:50,113
Become a part of the political system..

1673
02:35:50,613 --> 02:35:57,196
This country will change..
We will change it!

1674
02:35:57,696 --> 02:35:59,113
If you believed the Defence Minister..

1675
02:35:59,613 --> 02:36:01,363
.. deserved to be punished then..

1676
02:36:01,863 --> 02:36:07,321
.. what about the allegations against your father?

1677
02:36:07,821 --> 02:36:11,196
Don't worry.. We'll find a way to fix this.

1678
02:36:11,696 --> 02:36:12,571
Is there any way out, Dad?

1679
02:36:13,071 --> 02:36:16,571
Of course, I am there, I will handle everything.

1680
02:36:32,780 --> 02:36:36,280
I'm sorry Dad..

1681
02:37:03,663 --> 02:37:06,738
My name is Daljeet Singh.

1682
02:37:07,238 --> 02:37:10,071
There are only two ways to live your life.

1683
02:37:10,571 --> 02:37:17,488
Tolerate things the way they are.

1684
02:37:17,988 --> 02:37:24,405
Or take responsibility to change them.

1685
02:37:24,905 --> 02:37:28,405
Karan Singhania killed his father
before coming here.

1686
02:37:37,155 --> 02:37:41,905
Shit DJ!

1687
02:37:42,105 --> 02:37:44,313
You're bleeding badly!

1688
02:37:45,113 --> 02:37:49,363
Relax!
It got tired of flowing in my veins.

1689
02:37:49,863 --> 02:37:52,946
It just wanted to be free.

1690
02:37:53,446 --> 02:37:56,571
Aslam.. Laxman.. Sukhi?

1691
02:37:57,071 --> 02:38:00,571
All gone.

1692
02:38:10,696 --> 02:38:17,321
.. Karan, I think I'm in love..

1693
02:38:17,821 --> 02:38:20,780
.. I never told you dude..

1694
02:38:21,280 --> 02:38:27,905
.. can't stop thinking about her..

1695
02:38:28,405 --> 02:38:32,780
I know..
she's something else.

1696
02:38:33,280 --> 02:38:36,780
You two'll make a great couple.

1697
02:38:41,196 --> 02:38:44,613
There's just one problem.
I don't know if...

1698
02:38:45,113 --> 02:38:48,613
